    title: 'Boat behaviour, measured — not inferred',
    body: 'Most trackers watch the athlete. We also watch the hull: trim, heel and yaw, stroke by stroke.',
  },
  {
    tag: 'Calibrated',
    title: 'Tuned to your body, not heart-rate zones',
    body: 'Analysis is anthropometry-aware, so a number means the same thing for every athlete who reads it.',
  },
  {
    tag: 'Accessible',
    title: 'A fraction of professional telemetry',
    body: 'One integrated system — sensor, app and analysis — at a price a club can actually reach.',
  },
  {
